task.summary:
Add initial project configuration files
- Create .gitignore to exclude IDE and local files - Add XML files for migration state services - Include index layout and version control settings

Add integration tests for note backfilling and CRUD operations
- Implement tests for backfilling tags for multiple users. - Add tests for periodic saving during tag backfilling. - Create integration tests for complete CRUD workflow of notes. - Ensure proper handling of updates and deletions in tests.

Add unit tests for SeedNotes and NoteEditor components
- Implement tests for seeding notes and backfilling tags. - Verify error handling for unauthenticated users. - Ensure successful creation and processing of notes. - Add performance tests for NoteEditor component.

Add unit tests for OpenAI edge cases in `FindRelatedNotesAsync`
- Add tests for null, zero, and invalid embeddings. - Test behavior with empty user ID and no notes in the database. - Validate ordering by similarity and TopN parameter handling. - Ensure filtering by user ID and exclusion of current notes. - Add test coverage for embeddings with null values.

Add unit tests for BackfillTagsHandler
- Implement tests for processing notes with and without tags. - Ensure exception handling for AI service failures. - Validate correct processing counts and error reporting.

Add seed data generation and related tests
- Introduce structured prompts for autonomy implementation and generation. - Implement SeedNotesHandler with methods for creating notes. - Add unit tests for SeedNotesHandler to verify functionality. - Ensure AI service methods are called correctly and handle failures gracefully.

Add DotSettings for WPF resource dictionary
Creates a new DotSettings file to define WPF resource dictionary settings for user dictionary entry indexing.

Add Qodana configuration file
Creates a new qodana.yaml file to configure Qodana analysis. Sets up inspection profiles and quality gate thresholds for CI/CD.

Update README with testing instructions and project details
- Added detailed instructions for running tests - Improved formatting and clarity in project structure section - Updated technology stack descriptions for consistency - Enhanced user isolation explanation for clarity

Organize project structure into folders
- Created a folder for source files under /SRC/ - Created a folder for test files under /Tests/ - Updated project paths in the solution file accordingly

Add ExcludeFromCodeCoverage attribute to test classes
- Mark test classes with [ExcludeFromCodeCoverage] to improve coverage reports. - Ensure that architecture and integration tests are excluded from coverage metrics. - Update namespaces for consistency across test files.

Refactor routing and update navigation menu
- Change namespace for IdentityComponentsEndpointRouteBuilderExtensions. - Update NavMenu to include a link for seeding demo notes. - Adjust MediatR registration to use the correct assembly reference.
